title: Hiroyoshi Tsukamoto - Super Manga Matrix [PDF, Epub & Mobi]
description:
Super Manga Matrix by Hiroyoshi Tsukamoto


The follow-up to the hugely popular Manga Matrix, Super Manga Matrix reveals an innovative Japanese arithmetic method to create stunning manga. Using simple addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division, readers will learn to create an infinite number of manga characters with unique physical attributes, costumes, skills, and personality types, as well as secondary characters that they can engage with in a manga story.
